## Data Source Attributions

This project integrates data from the following APIs:

- **CoinGecko API** - [Terms of Service](https://www.coingecko.com/en/api_terms)
- **Frankfurter API** - [GitHub](https://github.com/hakanensari/frankfurter)
- **Infura** - [Terms of Service](https://infura.io/terms)
- **Various Blockchain RPCs** - See individual chain documentation

Users of this software are responsible for complying with the terms of service of these data providers.

